blocks.block_text: " The bhanas are as a rule deal with the social and moral drawbacks of the people with a view to give the people an opportunity to rectify themselves . All the bhanas are devoted to the elucidation of the ways of inumoral conjugal happiness . So that the people may detect those means and put a stop to them ( అనంగ జీవనము వ్రాతప్రతికి ఉపోద్ఘాతము . )
lines: " The bhanas are as a rule deal with the social and moral drawbacks of the people with a view to give the people an opportunity to rectify themselves . All the bhanas are devoted to the elucidation of the ways of inumoral conjugal happiness . So that the people may detect those means and put a stop to them ( అనంగ జీవనము వ్రాతప్రతికి ఉపోద్ఘాతము . )
